737
00:40:31,400 --> 00:40:32,630
I didn’t lie to her.

738
00:40:33,800 --> 00:40:34,670
I didn’t.

739
00:40:34,680 --> 00:40:36,110
I didn’t lie to her.

740
00:40:38,240 --> 00:40:39,710
I don't remember

741
00:40:41,240 --> 00:40:42,520
